{"tid":1906721,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"捱催淚彈拍攝 《手足》柏林有迴響","createTime":"2020-03-02T06:19:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-03T09:04:00.000Z","uid":25558,"like":46,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"b660374479cf098c73dbfc74683f417950a4cd34","tid":1906721,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T06:19:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200302/C2SVBPZPT625A2DAJMXD4OKOAU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200302%2FC2SVBPZPT625A2DAJMXD4OKOAU%2F&d=cG87S%2FC0TFnLRhO0hL0igUYZmLIq74JPLN0FyuDKESI%3D&h=f8bdda34\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200302%2FC2SVBPZPT625A2DAJMXD4OKOAU%2F&h=59e6f80b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200302/C2SVBPZPT625A2DAJMXD4OKOAU/</a><br />\n<br />\n捱催淚彈拍攝 《手足》柏林有迴響<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200302/large/1583069410_b2c5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200302%2Flarge%2F1583069410_b2c5.jpg&h=f0d940ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《手足》展現前線示威者對抗警察時的默契與團結。<br />\n<br />\n第70屆柏林影展昨日落幕，香港短篇電影《手足》入圍新生代單元（Generation 14plus），短片內容記錄香港去年的逆權運動。雖然短片最後敗給加拿大/摩洛哥電影《Mutts》，未能贏得水晶熊獎，但已引來世界迴響。導演廖潔雯接受德國《德國之聲》記者訪問，她表示去年6月想為反送中運動出一分力，因此與朋友拿起攝錄機，記錄這場民主運動。《手足》記錄去年7月28日西環事件，見到各不相識的年輕人之間的默契、包容與團結，並在國家機器的打壓下變成「手足」。廖潔雯又指拍攝時，不但被催淚彈襲擊，耳邊不停有橡膠子彈飛過。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：彭浩翔撞臉落單拔槍警<br />\n<br />\n攝影師鄭焯航則表示，前線示威者以身體對抗警察，讓世界看到了香港警察怎樣對付追求民主自由的人。團隊成員也把印上五大訴求的明信片帶到放映現場，向觀眾解釋這場香港民主運動。<br />\n<br />\n撰文︰祖李<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200302/large/1583069408_873a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200302%2Flarge%2F1583069408_873a.jpg&h=e8d3805a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《手足》記錄去年7月28日一天內發生的事件，團隊拍攝時食了不少催淚彈。劇照<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200302/large/1583069409_31fe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200302%2Flarge%2F1583069409_31fe.jpg&h=a7f5a41f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n導演廖潔雯日前接受德國傳媒訪問，透露拍攝短篇電影目的是想為運動出一分力。互聯網圖片"},{"pid":"8d906259be2ee5b333d9c4112c692f2109d3ed27","tid":1906721,"uid":160637,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T07:03:19.000Z","msg":"相關新聞：彭浩翔撞臉落單拔槍警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b19cec68e2cbd729a5b4032c22cdd7dc6cf3e31f","tid":1906721,"uid":8582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T01:25:28.000Z","msg":"風雨雲巴打做咗個專訪<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ntthCgX\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ntthCgX</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e05d00794376244dbcffc1b79646a8a2ce922b92","tid":1906721,"uid":62749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T01:31:54.000Z","msg":"國際文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3de9affc8e4f801cb6ecf9be331a2be08be366b2","tid":1906721,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T01:38:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2f70c24a96d930f8db45f37d71ebe72d6e4a4d2","tid":1906721,"uid":560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T01:44:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"851728f50